'''Djamal Mohamed''' (born October 8, 1990 in [[Marseille]], [[France]]) is a French-born Comorian footballer who has 2 caps for the Comoros National Football Team.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goal.com/en/people/france/63968/djamal-mohamed/national|title=Djamal Mohamed|website=Goal.com|accessdate=15 January 2012}}</ref>
