{{about|Hogan Stand magazine and website|the stand in Croke Park|Croke Park}}
'''''Hogan Stand''''' is a [[Gaelic games]] magazine, published monthly and distributed throughout [[Ireland]]. The magazine is named after the main stand in [[Croke Park]], where the trophies are presented to the winning captains.The magazine was founded in 1991.<ref>{{cite book|author=Prasidh Kumar Mishra|title=Sports Journalism|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Jcfml8Fqy1wC&pg=PT145|accessdate=16 August 2015|date=10 October 2010|publisher=Pinnacle Technology|isbn=978-1-61820-463-9|page=145}}</ref>

