{{National rugby union | unionname = Rugby Union of Bosnia and Herzegovina | nativename = Ragbi Savez Bosne i Hercegovine | logo = Ragbibih.jpg | imagesize = 150px | founded = 1992 | IRB = 1996 | region = [[FIRA - Association of European Rugby|RE]] | regionyear = 1992 | president = Semir Mahić | coach = Ermin Mušinović }} The '''Rugby Union of Bosnia and Herzegovina''' ({{lang-bs|Ragbi Savez Bosne i Hercegovine}}) is the governing body for [[Rugby union|rugby]] in Bosnia and Herzegovina. It oversees the various national teams and domestic competitions.
