'''SK Futures Park''' is a [[baseball stadium]] in [[Incheon]], [[South Korea]]. The stadium was completed in 2015 and is used by the [[KBO Futures League]] team [[SK Wyverns]]. The original training stadium of the SK Wyverns was located in the [[Nam District, Incheon|Nam District]] of Incheon and was named '''SK Dream Park'''. It was built in 2001 and demolished in 2006.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://sports.news.naver.com/general/news/read.nhn?oid=038&aid=0000066893|publisher=''Naver''|date=23 April 2001|accessdate=1 May 2017|language=ko|title=[프로야구 SK] 드림파크 24일 개관}}</ref>

