'''Sarpugerði''' is a [[stadium]] in [[Norðragøta]], [[Faroe Islands]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Víkingur Gøta]] and has a capacity of 1,600 (440 seated).<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nordicstadiums.com/sarpugerdi/ | title=Sarpugerði| accessdate=13 July 2018}}</ref>
