'''[[Thailand]]''' competed at the '''[[1960 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Rome]], [[Italy]]. Twenty competitors, all men, took part in sixteen events in four sports.<ref name="SportsRef">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/THA/summer/1960/ |title=Thailand at the 1960 Rome Summer Games |accessdate=21 June 2015 |work=Sports Reference}}</ref>
